
Survey Form
This is a simple survey form webpage built using HTML and CSS.

Features
Collects user information such as name, email, age, current status, gender, skills, and comments/suggestions.
All fields marked with a red asterisk (*) are required.
Provides dropdown menus, radio buttons, checkboxes, and a textarea for user input.
Includes a submit button to submit the form.
Usage
Clone the repository or download the HTML and CSS files.
Open the index.html file in a web browser.
Fill in the form fields with the required information.
Optionally, provide any comments or suggestions in the textarea field.
Click the "Submit" button to submit the form.
Customization
You can customize the form and its appearance by modifying the HTML and CSS code. Here are a few suggestions:

Modify the form labels, placeholders, and options to suit your specific survey requirements.
Adjust the styling by editing the style.css file. You can change colors, fonts, dimensions, and alignments to match your desired design.
Dependencies
This project has no external dependencies. It only requires a web browser to run the HTML file.

